Let's get started with creating your dream WordPress website.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What do I need to get started?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: It'll depend on your project, Common for every project if new website must need Domain & Hosting Cpanel login, and if already have installed WordPress then just WordPress login(some case Cpanel/FTP). Just leave a message brief about your project, I will assist you with what you need for your project

questionsAndAnswers.question: Why WordPress?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: You will happy to know today 25% of the world's websites run on Wordpress and the most interesting thing is WordPress Is 99% SEO Friendly according to Google also WordPress is User-Friendly & High-security standard.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide domain and hosting?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: No, You need to get domain/hosting and provide us the access for Its control panel. I will assist  you for entire process how you can purchase domain and hosting.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will I be able to add, edit, update products myself?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, you can. it's very easy just a doing blog post. and the good news is in woocommerce have a great document for adding a product, category, subcategory, images, and colors etc. Here is the document https://docs.woocommerce.com/document/managing-products

questionsAndAnswers.question: Don't have any Idea about Website, Theme or Design?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Don't worry about this, I'll assist You. Please send a message about your website topic and services. Then I'll manage the entire journey.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What type of website do you build?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I can build any type of website form Custom Website to Blog, Newspaper, Portfolio, Hotels, Agency, Sports, Business, Corporates, Company portfolio, Real Estate, Online Store, E-commerce, Education, Event, Wedding, Affiliate, Lading page, Directory listing, Job portal, Restaurants, GYM and Many more.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you have any portfolio of your recent work?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I have a portfolio website in this i have added my all recent delivery websites you can check it here: wpexpertfiroz.me . also, If you want to see my recent delivery work portfolios please send and message.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide support after completing the job?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I will provide free 30 day hand holding support after complete the job, so you don't need to think about support.

questionsAndAnswers.question: If I'll unhappy with your work or design.
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I'm trying my best to make you satisfy Unless you are 100% Satisfied, still, I'll make you unhappy you will get 100% full payment refund.

reviews.comment: Working with Firoz was adequate, but there were several issues that stood out. While his services are affordable and he communicates his needs clearly, the work lacked attention to detail, took longer than expected, and didn't quite meet what was promised. Additionally, his informal communication style and excuses for delays made the collaboration less professional at times.

This guy is incredibly skilled. Time and time again, he delivers exceptional service, quality, and a genuine passion for working with the finer details. His expertise has helped me so much, and he’s by far the most patient person I’ve ever encountered on Fiverr. He keeps working until you’re completely satisfied. So, thank you once again for the collaboration. This definitely won’t be the last time I work with him!
I have worked many times with this developer. Always experience kindness, professionalism and skills. Thanks again for your service.
really amazing. helped me beyond my expectations
